text: Daisy Jessica Edgar-Jones (born 24 May 1998) is an English actress. She is best known for her role as Marianne in the miniseries Normal People (2020). Her other television work includes Cold Feet (2016–2020) and War of the Worlds (2019–2021). She is also known for her role as Kate in the 2024 disaster movie Twisters. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:English movie actors Category:English television actors Category:English stage actors Category:English voice actors Category:Actors from London
